---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Info — Explicit Studio">

  <!-- Studio Philosophy -->
  <section class="info-philosophy reveal">
    <h1 class="info-philosophy__headline">We hate boring stories.</h1>
    <div class="info-philosophy__body">
      <p>Look hard enough and there's something interesting about everything, including B2B SaaS. Unfortunately, somewhere along the way, tech startups developed a storytelling problem. Code isn't the differentiator it used to be. And while everyone talks about narratives and taste, everything still looks the same.</p>
      <p>We believe tech will become the consumer brands of tomorrow. Which means, it can't just be functional anymore. It has to mean something. It has to make people feel something.</p>
      <p>Explicit lives at the intersection of art & technology to help startups evoke magic, joy & a sense of wonder and optimism through storytelling, brand and creativity.</p>
      <p><strong>You've made something the world needs. Make it Explicit.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We Believe -->
  <section class="info-beliefs reveal">
    <h2 class="info-beliefs__title">We Believe</h2>
    <div class="info-beliefs__list">
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>Tech is culture.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>The story is part of the product.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>A good story is a business advantage.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>Startups die when they stop taking creative risk.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Srijan -->
  <section class="info-about reveal">
    <div class="info-about__grid">
      <div class="info-about__body">
        <p>I'm Srijan. I've spent my entire life thinking about what makes people pay attention & build trust.</p>
        <p>It began when I started playing music when I was 15. Somewhere along the way, I became the drummer for Parikrama, Shubha Mudgal & a bunch of other bands. I played more than a 1000 concerts around the world & toured with Iron Maiden apart from playing at The Kennedy Centre. I also worked on films and advertising, spending years learning how stories work, what makes them stick, and what makes them forgettable.</p>
        <p>A few years ago, I started building startups & built Pause & Attis.</p>
        <p>You can learn more about me on my <a href="https://srijanmahajan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">website</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-about__portrait">
        <img src="/images/srijan-portrait.JPG" alt="Srijan Mahajan" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="info-services reveal">
    <div class="info-services__inner">
      <h2 class="info-services__title">How We Work</h2>
      <div class="info-services__intro">
        <p>Explicit doesn't have account managers, elaborate processes, or bloated teams. You talk to me & my little gold book of collaborators of designers, developers, copywriters, motion artists, and strategists. We understand your startup, we move fast, and we build things that work. No scope creep, no surprise invoices, no design-by-committee.</p>
        <p><strong>We work with a maximum of 3 clients per quarter.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-services__offers">
        <div class="info-services__offer">
          <h3>Storytelling Sprint — 6 Weeks</h3>
          <p class="info-services__offer-sub">Everything you need to go from unknown to unforgettable.</p>
          <p class="info-services__offer-label">What you walk away with:</p>
          <div class="info-services__deliverables">
            <p>&rarr; Brand positioning document</p>
            <p>&rarr; Complete narrative & messaging framework</p>
            <p>&rarr; Brand identity & visual system</p>
            <p>&rarr; Designed and developed website</p>
            <p>&rarr; 90-day content strategy</p>
            <p>&rarr; Brand guidelines</p>
            <p>&rarr; 30 days of post-launch support</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-services__offer">
          <h3>Monthly Partnership — Ongoing</h3>
          <p class="info-services__offer-sub">An ongoing creative partner for the work that comes after launch.</p>
          <div class="info-services__deliverables">
            <p>&rarr; GTM strategy and campaign architecture</p>
            <p>&rarr; Advertising creatives and copy</p>
            <p>&rarr; Viral campaign concepts and execution</p>
            <p>&rarr; Content strategy and production</p>
            <p>&rarr; Weekly syncs — no ticket systems, no queues</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="info-faq reveal">
    <div class="info-faq__list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What kind of startups do you work with?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We work with ambitious founders in AI, Crypto, Healthcare & D2C. If you believe creativity is a business advantage and you're not looking for safe work, we should talk.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          How much does it cost?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>It depends on the scope. Get in touch and we'll figure out if there's a fit before talking numbers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What's your process?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We start with strategy; understanding your market, competition, and unfair advantages. Then we build the brand, web & content. Our Storytelling Sprint is 6 weeks end-to-end. Monthly partnerships are ongoing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Do you do just websites? Just logos?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We work best when we do everything from brand strategy to execution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Philosophy ===== */
  .info-philosophy {
    padding: 40px var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-philosophy__headline {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-philosophy__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ===== We Believe ===== */
  .info-beliefs {
    padding: 0 var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-beliefs__title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-beliefs__list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .info-beliefs__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 24px 0;
  }

  .info-beliefs__item h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ===== About Srijan ===== */
  .info-about {
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .info-about__body p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-about__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-about__body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-about__body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .info-about__portrait {
    position: sticky;
    top: 40px;
  }

  .info-about__portrait img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  /* ===== How We Work ===== */
  .info-services {
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-services__title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-services__inner {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .info-services__intro {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .info-services__intro p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .info-services__intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-services__intro strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .info-services__offers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .info-services__offer {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px);
  }

  .info-services__offer h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .info-services__offer-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .info-services__offer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .info-services__deliverables p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ===== FAQ ===== */
  .info-faq {
    padding: 0 var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-faq__list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .faq-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .info-cta {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-cta__inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .info-cta__inner h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .info-cta__button {
    padding: 16px 40px;
  }

  .info-cta__email {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-cta__email:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .info-about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .info-about__portrait {
      position: static;
      order: -1;
    }

    .info-services__offer {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .info-beliefs__item h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-h3);
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // FAQ accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach((btn) => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      btn.closest('.faq-item')?.classList.toggle('open');
    });
  });

  // Scroll reveal
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1 }
  );

  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
